Livin' in a box by Cybernetic Genetics

OpenCV, Freenect was heavily used during making this demo.
Yes, Revision 2012 organizers thought this demo no good
enough to show it.

Tested on Ubuntu 11.04, Ubuntu 12.04 (64bit). To run it you
need an OpenGL 4.1 capable card.

Source code included under GPL licence.

